id": "178841301831188", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974904_178841305164521_6240061712629683638_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=9n0OeupegF4Q7kNvgGoKPK_&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAcyV9pKx2IkB3qUGo3D2VWPlQBjVc4EPg3gYBvqKRV9Q&oe=66FBF77A"}, {"file_name": "6_Lux_Black.png", "id": "204260489327069", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974788_204260495993735_3013857851470971529_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hcVYT1HVYc8Q7kNvgGkycvo&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCjK6_Byc5dJAzhZkUt5F0ze5CKgAihyqdG-V_S8M2R4g&oe=66FBCE39"}, {"file_name": "2_OrangeGuy.png", "id": "821334719782339", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031376_821334723115672_497413205435619889_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7ZQzM1_exTcQ7kNvgFgAouv&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCEVBsn8TXXxdjud-3_VQoliM2uYXvRaCfSjqbrxMWb0Q&oe=66FBDD72"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Fitness One XR Evolved", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Forget tedious fitness apps and videos: With Fitness One XR, you bring the personal trainer experience, once reserved for the elite, right into your home!\n\nWhether you're looking to improve your health, enhance your posture, strengthen your back, power up your heart, sculpt a six-pack, a round booty and sleek legs, boost your endurance, sharpen your memory, build more muscle, strengthen your arms, foster a positive attitude, or simply enjoy working out to music with today\u2019s best trainer: Fitness One XR is here for you.\n\nFitness One XR offers over a hundred fitness programs: from cardio to strengthening and sculpting every single muscle group. Thanks to cutting-edge technology, now you can enjoy working out alongside a challenging personal trainer who\u2019s always there for you, continually motivating you to work on self-improvement.\n\nWith over a thousand options to customize your own realistic personal trainer and the most advanced, innovative AI techniques assisting you to swiftly become healthier, stronger, more attractive, and more vibrant, this is the most comprehensive XR fitness experience available.\n\nFitness One is the only XR app offering exercises for literally every muscle group; and together with our unparalleled, years of R&D perfected form-tracking, your workout just became way more effective. Thousands of users have already joined, with an average cross-platform customer rating of 9 so far.\n\nExperience the difference yourself, and try Fitness One XR - Evolved today!", "short_description": "The most effective and motivating way to become healthier, stronger, and more attractive: The elite personal trainer experience, now available to you!\n\nWhether you're looking to improve your health, enhance your posture, strengthen your back, power up your heart, sculpt a six-pack, a round booty and sleek legs, boost your endurance, build more muscle, strengthen your arms, foster a positive attitude, or simply enjoy working out to music with today\u2019s best trainer: Fitness One XR is here for you!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://fitnesscloud.eu/privacyPolicy.htm", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://fitnesscloud.eu/eula.htm", "publisher_name": "Verseus Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.verseus-games.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3362542290449643"}, {"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "619566195371476"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "de"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], 